[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[ PowerShell Basic Commands ]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]


Get-Command *

[Gets list of all commands]

--------

Get-Command *connection*

[Gets list of commands with the string "connection"]

--------

Get-Help Stop-Process

[Shows description of "Stop-Process" command (like manpages in Linux)]

-------

Get-Help Stop-Process -Examples

[Shows examples of "Stop-Process" command]

--------

Get-Help Stop-Process -Examples

[Shows examples of "Stop-Process" command]

--------

Get-TimeZone

[Shows local machine timezone]

--------

Get-Date

[Shows systems date]

--------

Get-Date | Format-List

[Shows system date but also shows it in a list of possible formats]

--------

Get-Random

[Shows random number]

--------

Get-Random | Get-Member

[Shows list of methods you can use with Get-Random object]

--------

Find-Module -Tag Telegram

[Searches additional modules (here "Telegram" modules) to PowerShell, that allows for extending PS functionalities]

--------

